title: TUESDAY -  MNF recap Goff outduels Brady 2020
itunes:title: TUESDAY -  MNF recap Goff outduels Brady 2020
description:
Monday Night Football (0:06) featured two of the premiere teams in the NFC as Jared Goff and the Rams outdueled Tom Brady and the Buccaneers. We'll hear from Goff on the big win (1:47). The Ravens will be short-handed Thursday night (2:18) as several key players land on the Reserve/COVID-19 list. Plus an update on Joe Burrow's injured knee (2:48)
